etomica.data

Class DataInfoFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.data.DataInfoFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEtomicaDataInfoFactory, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataDouble.DataInfoDoubleFactory, DataDoubleArray.DataInfoDoubleArrayFactory, DataDoubleBDArray.DataInfoDoubleBDArrayFactory, DataGroup.DataInfoGroupFactory, DataTensor.DataInfoTensorFactory, DataVector.DataInfoVectorFactory

    public abstract class DataInfoFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, IEtomicaDataInfoFactory
    Interface for a mutable DataInfo factory. The factory is created based on an existing DataInfo object, but can be modified before being used to create new DataInfo objects.
    See Also:
